  "2215540": {
    "name": "Colossal Cave",
    "steam_appid": 2215540,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/d4129a330c783040f8b838b95cb174fe.poster.avif?t=1769647910\" width=616 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/d4129a330c783040f8b838b95cb174fe.webm?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/d4129a330c783040f8b838b95cb174fe.mp4?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>踏上一次超越时空的旅程，探索庞大的洞穴系统，这里充满了宝藏、生物、迷宫和令人绞尽脑汁的谜题。这款冒险游戏的鼻祖将考验你的智慧和解谜能力，伴随着你逐步揭开游戏的剧情与秘密。通过不断的尝试与失败，你将穿越狭窄的缝隙、进入令人惊叹的洞窟、收集物品、寻找宝藏、抵御矮人的攻击——并在你的灯熄灭之前，盯紧得分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把你上世纪七八十年代的《Colossal Cave》老地图翻出来吧，它们依旧管用。这是一款忠实还原原始设计的致敬之作。需要一点提示？被龙卡住了吗？拨打我们的<i>经典提示热线</i>：<strong>1-206-207-9017</strong> 获取帮助。还在苦苦挣扎？上网搜索几十年来积累的攻略和窍门。原版的所有技巧在这里依然适用。或者加入我们的 Discord 社区，获取更多支持！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/036df3a5dca425a90117d461bcd84a31.poster.avif?t=1769647910\" width=616 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/036df3a5dca425a90117d461bcd84a31.webm?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/036df3a5dca425a90117d461bcd84a31.mp4?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/b83469709ab75674435de739eac139b5.poster.avif?t=1769647910\" width=616 height=42 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/b83469709ab75674435de739eac139b5.webm?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/b83469709ab75674435de739eac139b5.mp4?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>这款文字冒险游戏由一位业余洞穴探险者在 1970 年代中期开发，最初只是想让他的两个女儿开心。Will Crowther 的设计灵感来源于他和妻子 Patricia 一起绘制的肯塔基州猛犸洞穴中 Bedquilt 区域的详细地图。家庭洞穴探险是本游戏的灵魂所在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不久之后，程序员兼“恶作剧专家”Don Woods 在 ARPANET 上发现了这款游戏，并将洞穴内容扩展。他加入了更多乐趣、幻想、谜题，以及一个复杂的 350 分系统。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多年后，Don 的版本成为了最广为流传、也被视为权威的<i>Colossal Cave Adventure</i>版本。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/9d8b4c39ed4307fe114478d4749f07e2.poster.avif?t=1769647910\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/9d8b4c39ed4307fe114478d4749f07e2.webm?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/9d8b4c39ed4307fe114478d4749f07e2.mp4?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/c0ccc5da935d8627ea1b15b2a2eeaa74.poster.avif?t=1769647910\" width=616 height=42 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/c0ccc5da935d8627ea1b15b2a2eeaa74.webm?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/c0ccc5da935d8627ea1b15b2a2eeaa74.mp4?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>接下来是 Roberta Williams 的登场。她在 1979 年首次接触这款游戏，立刻爱上了它。她花了数周时间反复游玩、做笔记、绘制地图，逐步还原洞穴中那些由文字描绘的奇景。她脑海中充满了虚幻的霓虹蘑菇、迷雾弥漫的地下湖泊、凶狠的双壳类软体动物，以及一个明显缺席的巨人。在完成所有 350 分的挑战后，她渴望更多的冒险——可在 1979 年，意味着她得自己创造！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她确实做到了。1980 年，她设计并开发了世界上首款图形冒险游戏：<i>Mystery House</i>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/c029eaacdc8401ecf23f1c42e34e2f45.poster.avif?t=1769647910\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/c029eaacdc8401ecf23f1c42e34e2f45.webm?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/c029eaacdc8401ecf23f1c42e34e2f45.mp4?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/3b9f76f24de09bac60406b83dc273fbf.poster.avif?t=1769647910\" width=616 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/3b9f76f24de09bac60406b83dc273fbf.webm?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/3b9f76f24de09bac60406b83dc273fbf.mp4?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>这款开创性的游戏被誉为游戏史上最具影响力的作品之一，奠定了冒险类游戏的基本标准。它几乎被移植到每一台电脑与主机上，数百万玩家沉浸其中，并启发了大量游戏、书籍、电影与电视剧的诞生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重温冒险游戏的黄金时代。沉浸在这场跨越时空的探险中，探索一个充满宝藏、生物和谜题的巨大洞穴系统。回到那个更单纯的时代，感受 point-and-click 操作的复古魅力，以及致敬经典风格的美术呈现。这部满载敬意与热爱的致敬作品由精品工作室 Cygnus Entertainment 精心打造。Ken 与 Roberta Williams 致力于分享并传承经典冒险游戏的精神。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/7ce862ba1ba2bf5e9e7a9297105b430d.poster.avif?t=1769647910\" width=616 height=42 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/7ce862ba1ba2bf5e9e7a9297105b430d.webm?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/7ce862ba1ba2bf5e9e7a9297105b430d.mp4?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>借助充满挑战且令人费解的谜题，这款探索类游戏会让你爱不释手。游戏包含 14 个独特区域，每个区域都充满魔法、隐藏的秘密、惊艳的场景以及形形色色的洞穴生物。每一处都带来独特且迷人的体验。加上超过 20 个成就等你发现与完成，你将沉浸数小时！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >简洁直观的 point-and-click 控制方式  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富多彩、沉浸感强的探索区域  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于逻辑的挑战性谜题  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完美平衡的挑战与回报  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隐藏秘密的地下美景  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过 20 个独立成就等待解锁  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >趣味十足、引人入胜的玩法  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独一无二的游戏体验  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/06e0f7abb4a56bc3ec685558c4d1f02c.poster.avif?t=1769647910\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/06e0f7abb4a56bc3ec685558c4d1f02c.webm?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/06e0f7abb4a56bc3ec685558c4d1f02c.mp4?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/566d90596578ce468e0c00b86125db1a.poster.avif?t=1769647910\" width=616 height=206 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/566d90596578ce468e0c00b86125db1a.webm?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215540/extras/566d90596578ce468e0c00b86125db1a.mp4?t=1769647910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然这款游戏深深扎根于游戏历史与文化之中，但它之所以能经受时间考验，并深深融入玩家社区的原因只有一个：它真的好玩！它也富有挑战与深度，既简单又复杂，极富创造性——正如 Roberta 所说：“它的设计太棒了。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入<i>Colossal Cave</i>，探索它深邃的秘密。别忘了带上你的灯！</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 意大利语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 日语, 波兰语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 泰语, 阿拉伯语, 韩语, 俄语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
